Privacy Policy for Beni Uyandır (Wake Me Up)

Last Updated: November 13, 2025

Beni Uyandır app uses your location only to trigger alarms.

**Data Collected:**
- Location information (stored only on device)
- Saved alarm locations

**Data Sharing:**
None of your data is shared with third parties or sent to our servers.

**Data Storage:**
All data is stored only on your device and is completely deleted when you uninstall the app.

**Location Usage:**
Location permission is only active when you start an alarm and automatically stops when you reach your destination. No location tracking occurs when alarm is not active.

**Background Usage:**
When alarm is active, we track your location in the background so we can wake you up even while sleeping. Background tracking stops when alarm is stopped.

**Contact:**
For privacy policy questions: hello.wakemeupapp@gmail.com
